OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOrkney will have a rather
OL,6,Fcloudy day with some occasional light
OL,7,Frain or drizzle. Shetland will be dry
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,9,Fsunny intervals.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith occasional light rain. Then the
OL,13,Frest of the night will remain cloudy
OL,14,Fwith a little light rain at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FMainly with variable amounts
OL,17,Fof cloud and just a few light showers,
OL,18,Fthese becoming more persistent later
OL,19,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
