OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fon Friday with occasional rain. Cloudy
OL,7,Fwith rain at first on Saturday, then
OL,8,Fdrier and eventually brighter in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,10,FSunday.
